svg:text.svg:tspan: Energy! Electricity! Radioactivity! GCSE Physics is packed with the punchiest topics
you can study. And this CGP book is the snappiest guide to the whole course —
we explain everything you need to know, with some off-kilter jokes as a bonus.
But that’s not all! There’s a raft of digital extras too, including step-by-step video
solutions from CGP’s experts, and brilliant quizzes that’ll
help the facts stick in your brain. It’s the best thing since the Big Bang.
